Class ALMultiParamTask

java.lang.Object
moa.AbstractMOAObject
moa.options.AbstractOptionHandler
moa.tasks.AbstractTask
moa.tasks.MainTask
moa.tasks.meta.MetaMainTask
moa.tasks.meta.ALMainTask
moa.tasks.meta.ALMultiParamTask
All Implemented Interfaces:
Configurable, Serializable, MOAObject, OptionHandler, Task
public class ALMultiParamTask
extends ALMainTask
This task individually evaluates an active learning classifier for each element of a set of parameter values. The individual evaluation is done by prequential evaluation (testing, then training with each example in sequence).
Version:
$Revision: 1 $
Author:
